headline: Erie Indemnity to host fourth quarter and year-end 2025 pre-recorded conference call and webcast
summary: Erie Indemnity Company (NASDAQ: ERIE) will host a pre-recorded audio webcast with the financial community providing financial results for the fourth quarter and year-end 2025 on Tuesday, February 24th, at 10 a.m. Eastern Time. Erie Indemnity will issue a press release reporting its results after the close of the market on Monday, February 23rd.

headline: Willis Towers Watson (WTW) Beats Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Willis Towers Watson (WTW) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +2.47% and +2.51%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
